<div id="post-402076" class="blog-post position-7 odd-post"><div class="odd-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/paulomarcos/blog/caldeirao-de-noticias-bahia-desta-quinta-feira-26">Caldeirão de Notícias Bahia desta quinta-feira, 26</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">Gennaio 26, 2012 0:00</span><span class="author">, by Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/paulomarcos/blog/caldeirao-de-noticias-bahia-desta-quinta-feira-26#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>no comments yet</span></a></span></span><p>Ouça aqui o Caldeirão de Notícias Bahia desta quarta-feira, 26.</p>
